Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.46,Caption,,0,0,0,,Thirty-seven seconds. That's all it\Ntook.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.80,0:00:07.40,Caption,,0,0,0,,Ten years of work. Around three hundred\Nand seventy
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.40,Caption,,0,0,0,,million dollars of rocket and\Nsatellites. Gone — over a
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.60,Caption,,0,0,0,,number that was too big for its box.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.94,0:00:18.06,Caption,,0,0,0,,An inquiry board took the failure apart.\NAnd the
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.06,0:00:21.52,Caption,,0,0,0,,uncomfortable truth is that no part of\Nthis was bad
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.52,0:00:24.63,Caption,,0,0,0,,luck. Every link in the chain was a\Ndecision.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.97,0:00:29.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,One. The navigation code was reused from\NAriane 4 without
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.08,0:00:32.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,being re-tested against Ariane 5's\Nactual flight profile.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.37,0:00:36.48,Caption,,0,0,0,,It was trusted because it had never\Nfailed — but
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.48,0:00:38.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,it had never flown this rocket.
